		/// <summary>Reads character input from the console input buffer and removes it from the buffer.</summary>
		/// <param name="hConsoleInput">A handle to the console input buffer. The handle must have the **GENERIC\_READ** access right. For more information, see [Console Buffer Security and Access Rights](console-buffer-security-and-access-rights.md).</param>
