/a> structure. This handle should be closed by the debugger application by calling the <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/api/handleapi/nf-handleapi-closehandle">CloseHandle</a> function. <div class="alert"><b>Warning</b>  Do not queue an <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/Sync/asynchronous-procedure-calls">asynchronous procedure call</a> (APC) to a thread that calls <b>WaitForDebugEventEx</b>.</div> <div> </div></para>
