		/// <para>If the function succeeds, it returns a nonzero value. If the function fails, it returns zero. To get extended error information, call <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/api/errhandlingapi/nf-errhandlingapi-getlasterror">GetLastError</a>.</para>
