ion has been called, the critical section object can no longer be used for synchronization. If a thread terminates while it has ownership of a critical section, the state of the critical section is undefined. To compile an application that uses this function, define <b>_WIN32_WINNT</b> as 0x0400 or later. For more information, see <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/WinProg/using-the-windows-headers">Using the Windows Headers</a>.</para>
