		/// <para>A pointer to a <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/api/winnt/ns-winnt-sid">SID</a> structure that represents the mandatory integrity level for the namespace. Use one of the following RID values to create the SID: <b>SECURITY_MANDATORY_UNTRUSTED_RID</b> <b>SECURITY_MANDATORY_LOW_RID</b> <b>SECURITY_MANDATORY_MEDIUM_RID</b> <b>SECURITY_MANDATORY_SYSTEM_RID</b> <b>SECURITY_MANDATORY_PROTECTED_PROCESS_RID</b> For more information, see <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/SecAuthZ/well-known-sids">Well-Known SIDs</a>.</para>
		/// <para><see href="https://learn.microsoft.com/windows/win32/api/winbase/nf-winbase-addintegritylabeltoboundarydescriptor#parameters">Read more on learn.microsoft.com</see>.</para>
