arks"></a><a id="security_remarks"></a><a id="SECURITY_REMARKS"></a>Security Remarks</h3> See <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/windows/desktop/Intl/security-considerations--international-features">Security Considerations: International Features</a> for security considerations regarding choice of comparison functions.</para>
